<span id="freeTextContainer5762692413806822895">I don&apos;t think there&apos;s really much left to say about Audre Lorde (especially by me, a random ass white lady). I&apos;ll just say that there&apos;s a reason that Audre Lorde is Audre Lorde, and if you ever need proof of that, just read <i>Sister Outsider</i>.<br/><br/>I don&apos;t think you can read anything by Lorde and not furiously scribble down what she&apos;s telling you, so here&apos;s one of my favorite quotes from this collection: “There are no new ideas. There are only new ways of making them felt.”<br/><br/>Audre Lorde makes you feel them</span>
  <span id="freeText5762692413806822895" style="display:none">I don't think there's really much left to say about Audre Lorde (especially by me, a random ass white lady). I'll just say that there's a reason that Audre Lorde is Audre Lorde, and if you ever need proof of that, just read <i>Sister Outsider</i>.<br /><br />I don't think you can read anything by Lorde and not furiously scribble down what she's telling you, so here's one of my favorite quotes from this collection: “There are no new ideas. There are only new ways of making them felt.”<br /><br />Audre Lorde makes you feel them viscerally.</span>
